Citation.sAuthor: Al-Kandary, J. A. M.[Jasem A. M.]
Citation.sTitle: Isobaric Vapor-Liquid Equilibria for Binary Mixtures of 1,2-Dibromoethane with Benzene, Toluene, Fluorobenzene, and Bromobenzene at Atmospheric Pressure
Citation.sAbstract: Vapor-liquid equilibria at atmospheric pressure for binary mixtures of 1,2-dibromoethane + benzene, + toluene, + fluorobenzene, and + bromobenzene have been determined. They have been correlated satisfactorily with the Wilson equation and have been shown to be thermodynamically consistent.
